			<div class="author">by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2570&amp;sid=1ef38e94a5f342a1481f4ca64fa3cf30">jojopi</a></strong> &raquo; Tue Nov 06, 2012 2:13 pm </div>

			

			<div class="content">Instead of checking the time repeatedly, you can sleep until (after) the beginning of the next second:<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: <a href="#" onclick="selectCode(this); return false;">Select all</a></dt><dd><code>sleep $(printf &quot;0.%09d&quot; $((1000000000-`date +%-N`)))</code></dd></dl></div>

			

